prompts.frontCover: A vibrant and dynamic comic book cover for a birthday card. The scene depicts a cartoon superhero, dramatically bursting out of a giant, beautifully wrapped birthday present. The wrapping paper, in bold primary colors like red and blue with yellow polka dots, is exploding outwards in jagged, stylized pieces. Confetti and streamers in bright, contrasting colors fill the air around the explosion. The superhero is striking a classic, powerful pose, one fist raised to the sky, with a huge, joyful grin. They are wearing a classic superhero costume with a cape that billows dynamically. In the center of the scene, integrated into the action, is the text "Have a SUPER Birthday!" written in a bold, yet elegant and readable, handwritten cursive script, outlined in a contrasting color to make it pop. The entire illustration is done in a flat 2D comic book style, featuring thick black outlines, Ben-Day dots for shading in some areas, and a palette of saturated, high-contrast colors. The background is a simple, bright yellow radial burst, emphasizing the explosive action. The composition is energetic, fun, and celebratory.
